import {React,useState,createContext} from 'react' import {useForm} from 'react-hook-form' import {yupResolver} from '@hookform/resolvers/yup' import * as yup from 'yup' import './Signup.css' const AppContext = createContext({}) const schema= yup.object().shape({ Fname:yup.string().required(), Lname:yup.string().required(), age:yup.string().required(), id:yup.string().required(), phone:yup.string().required(), email:yup.string().email().required(), Spassword:yup.string().min(4).max(16).required(), Cpassword:yup.string().oneOf([yup.ref("Spassword"),null]) }) const Signup = () => { const [userInfo,setUserInfo] = useState() const {register,handleSubmit,formState:{errors}} = useForm({ resolver:yupResolver(schema) }) const onSubmit =(data)=>{ setUserInfo(data) } return (

Sign Up Form

{JSON.stringify(userInfo,undefined,2)}

{errors.Fname?.message}

{errors.Lname?.message}

{errors.age?.message}

{errors.id?.message}

{errors.phone?.message}

{errors.email?.message}

{errors.Spassword && "Passowrd Should be more than 4 characters"}

{errors.Cpassword && "Passwords Should Match"}

 ) } export default Signup
